Comment: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:01.04,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,————————OPJP————————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:14.59,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Naked  Dive！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:30.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いったい何が正解なんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:33.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}タイムラインに咲き乱れるFAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:34.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What  is  reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:39.07,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絶望や歓喜なんて  駆け抜けるだけのMirage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:42.04,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}溢れるインフォメーション  揺らいでいるノンフィクション
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:45.12,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赤い冷静  青い情熱  曖昧な審判（ジャッジ）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:46.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見透かしちゃうジーザス飼い馴らし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:48.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無関心ヴィーナス気取ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:51.21,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}迷走幻想Highway…Seek  your  way！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:52.67,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Inside  Noside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:57.26,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}溺れていたいんでしょ  妄想はいつだって蜜の味
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:58.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Outside  Noside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:03.26,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それじゃ物足んないなら…「本能」（はだ）を曝せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:06.27,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}さぁ、Naked  Dive！感情を放って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:09.27,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確かめろ君のREALを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:12.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう、Naked  Dive！衝動のMyself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:15.44,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求め続ければいいんじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:18.61,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Making  your  world！！  無我夢中で叫べ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:21.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing  your  world！！  限界はないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:24.74,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Making  your  world！！  その真理（こたえ）の先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:28.37,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing  your  world！！  拓けNew  world！
Comment: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:01.12,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,————————OPCN————————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.46,0:01:14.59,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Naked  Dive！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.15,0:01:30.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}究竟何為正解？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:33.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在時間線上爭奇鬥豔的虛假
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:34.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What  is  reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:39.07,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕望和歡喜  只不過是穿插而過的幻景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:42.04,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}滿溢而出的資訊  搖搖欲墜的認知
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:45.12,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}紅色代表冷靜  藍色代表熱情  這曖昧不清的判定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:46.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}掌控洞悉一切的耶穌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:48.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}假冒冰冷美豔的維納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:51.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}迷茫幻想Highway…Seek  your  way！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:52.67,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Inside  Noside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:57.26,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想要沉溺於其中吧  妄想無論何時都如蜜之味
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:58.76,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Outside  Noside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:03.26,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}若是還不夠的話…那就把「本能」都展現出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:06.27,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來吧  Naked  Dive！  將感情釋放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:09.27,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去確定屬於你的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:12.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯  Naked  Dive！  不斷追尋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:15.44,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}屬於自己內心的那份衝動不就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:18.61,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Making  your  world！！  盡情地呼喊吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:21.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing  your  world！！  沒有任何界限
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:24.74,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Making  your  world！！  邁向那片真理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:28.37,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Changing  your  world！！  開拓新的世界！
Comment: 0,0:22:10.04,0:22:10.08,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,————————EDJP————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:16.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,新しいわたしで どんなときも向き合いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.34,0:22:19.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,みんなで笑顔になれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.98,0:22:32.64,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,好きなことができてたって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.64,0:22:37.44,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,一方通行じゃやっぱ ものたりないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.44,0:22:40.40,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,誰かに伝えたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.53,0:22:43.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,嬉しすぎると泣けちゃうし
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.41,0:22:45.95,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,悲しすぎると笑っちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:50.54,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,そんな毎日にトクンてきてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:53.54,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ぼんやりふくらんだ夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:56.29,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,きっとすぐ破裂しちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:22:59.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,悔しかったあの日のPain　(No need!)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.67,0:23:02.22,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,掴むべきは　これからのShine　(Yes!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:04.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,そう　(Yes!)　叶えるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:06.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ぜったいにできるって！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:08.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,鳥が空とぶように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:12.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,星が夜をかざるように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:14.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,当たり前みたいに いつも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:17.61,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,誰かに見てもらいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:19.48,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ひとりじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:25.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,真っ白なこころで迎えた朝は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.53,0:23:25.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,ハツラツだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.32,0:23:28.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}だから元気をおくろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:31.37,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\fad(200,0)}All right!　変わってく景色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:34.00,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}Always!　一緒にみたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:36.75,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}All right!　もちろん全力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:39.63,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\fad(0,200)}Always!　純真で　It's all right!
Comment: 0,0:22:10.04,0:22:10.08,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,————————EDCN————————
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:16.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,想无时无刻以全新的自己面对一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.34,0:22:19.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起冁然而笑吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.98,0:22:32.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,对于爱不释手的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.64,0:22:37.44,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,光是独享 果然是远远不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.44,0:22:40.40,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,想要将其分享给别人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.53,0:22:43.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,喜极而泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.41,0:22:45.95,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,悲中苦笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:50.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,每一天都令人期待不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:53.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,不明不白膨胀的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:56.29,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会马上破灭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:22:59.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,后悔过去的痛苦 （没必要！）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.67,0:23:02.22,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,该牢牢握住的是未来的曙光 （Yes!）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:04.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 （Yes!） 一定能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:06.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,必定会成功
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:08.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,如同翱翔于天际的小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.89,0:23:12.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛点缀于夜空的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.27,0:23:14.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,无论何时都理所当然地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.89,0:23:17.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,想要让别人也一起欣赏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.61,0:23:19.48,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,并非孤独一人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:25.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,以纯白内心所迎接的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.53,0:23:25.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么令人精力充沛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.32,0:23:28.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)}所以  想将活力赠于你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:31.37,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\fad(200,0)}All  right!  不断变化的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:34.00,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}Always!  想要与你一起观赏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:36.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}All  right!  当然会全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.75,0:23:39.63,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\fad(0,200)}Always!  维持纯真便行了!
Comment: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:01.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,————————Text————————
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海水浴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝉鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼屋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说夏天的代表性事物数不胜数
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若要说其中最让人兴奋的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  就是烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.05,0:00:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟  花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本在江户时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会放烟花来悼念因饥荒和瘟疫而去世的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及祈福身体的健康
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这据说就是烟花大会的起源
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从以前就有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然现在通过电视转播也能观看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.67,0:00:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过亲临会场观赏的感动是无与伦比的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.20,0:00:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音  震动  气味的临场感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,临场感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及  和同伴一起观赏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪耀在夜空中的烟花所带来的共鸣感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共鸣感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身处这特殊的感觉之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时说不出口的话也能说出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于现充们来说  是夏季约会的例行项目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:00:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现充
Comment: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:32.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,————————Text————————
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领带
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领带在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的烟花大会  小摊也会有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.84,0:02:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刨冰  章鱼小丸子  苹果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有波子汽水！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是把小玻璃珠压进去的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波子汽水是绝对不能错过的对吧  晴…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:54.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,…彦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.00,0:03:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太小了  我没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招  这样就能看见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了糟了  要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  身体小确实有些地方不方便呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢的波子汽水也没法一下喝完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果变大的话  就能把一瓶波子汽水全部喝完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像有什么愿望对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来实现你的愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是什么可疑人物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那么可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  我是善良的魔女phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是  稍微有点另类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在到处帮phantom们实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会有那么好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是以缩短寿命为代价来实现愿望之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替phantom实现愿望是我的存在意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会好好实现你的愿望的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没有陷阱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女绝不食言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就请你帮我实现愿望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  非常乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你的愿望是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让身体变成人类大小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  要是变成人类大小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能像现在这样飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  人类要是在天上飞也不太合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被别人发现你真实身份的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就会立刻变回原来的大小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  说起来小糸对phantom的气息非常敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被她发现不就全完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括这个在内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你变成人类后的各种设定我都会为你服务周到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请放心地变大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  开始了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,phan-phan-phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快变大  快变大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好厉害啊  魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  恭祝你得到好身材
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:40.40,English,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1035,952.5)}have  a  nice  body
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:42.25,English,NTP,0,0,0,,have  a  nice  day
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  回到座位上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:06:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们班有位转校生过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转校生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是男生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是漂亮的设定啊  魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请自我介绍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我介绍？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  首先是名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女  名字能自由发挥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  名字名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&H680B88&\4c&H2D042B&}夏野  夏野罗梦音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.77,TIPS1,NTP,0,0,0,,注：发音和「夏のラムネ」，「夏天的波子汽水」一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那么夏野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就坐在那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一条  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在晴彦的旁边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:06:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  不能飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  我经常会摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多关照  夏野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没露馅  没露馅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得夏野同学很像露露吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢  完全不像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏野同学更可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  好气人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏野同学  要是有什么不懂的就告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持续了大约十年的应仁之乱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使室町幕府的势力没落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后  强大的战国大名得以崛起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去散会步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在上课  不能去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏野同学  下节课要换教室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物理教室是在一楼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧  夏野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:07:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是自由奔放的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏野同学  要加入网球部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来新体操部参观吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必加入我们落语研究会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请一定来乒乓球部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都好有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:17.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社团邀约
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟夏野同学那么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦  也去邀请她加入我们社团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏野同学说了她不是特异能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  My  racket（我的球拍）去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来  我想去晴…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去一条的社团
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  但是夏野同学你不是特异能力者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活动室在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和晴彦并排走路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这种感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是活动室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女孩是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是晴彦他们班新来的转校生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然夏野同学不是特异能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过她想来看一下  所以我就带她来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是顾问姬野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请慢慢参观
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是高二的川神舞学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是小学部的熊枕久瑠美和阿尔布雷希特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高一的和泉玲奈和水无濑小糸同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会被小糸发现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏野同学  你以前是哪个学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对父母的事一点都没印象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.51,0:10:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在我出生半年前  就都去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身世自动就说出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女  干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果出生半年前妈妈就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那夏野同学不就不会存在了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是半年后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管如何都好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  魔女你认真点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北至北海道  南到冲绳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直被亲戚们当包袱扔来扔去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人被抛弃在这冷漠的世间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:31.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了活下去  连违法的事也做过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于这种生活我已精疲力尽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待我的只有横尸街头  就在我要放弃之时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇见了一直在寻找我的爷爷奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何等的令人感动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被发现了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦了你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连小糸也瞒过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然很棒啊  魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情享受学校生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把之前受的苦都补回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天正好是烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人多的地方phantom也容易出没
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起去玩  顺便巡视吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起去烟花大会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.02,0:11:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴衣  浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是从日本舞蹈部借来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.68,0:11:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了玲奈会穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.97,0:11:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天露露去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前不是一直都很期待烟花大会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露就是一直和晴彦在一起的phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个啊  今天早上我踩到了她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计在为此生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.14,0:11:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踩到了她？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好过分  晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心  那家伙很结实的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在烟花开始放之前会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说了  波子汽水是绝对不能错过的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露  能早点来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花大会上有想做的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  去小摊上吃刨冰  章鱼小丸子  苹果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在哪里听过…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有波子汽水！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK  一个个全都吃个遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.15,0:12:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一下喝完一瓶波子汽水之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要避免自己的身份暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是由烟花球变为付丧神的phantom吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像有什么愿望对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的这个愿望  由我魔女phantom来帮你实现
Comment: 0,0:13:18.05,0:13:18.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,————————Text————————
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人好多啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光走起来都很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到卖刨冰的了  夏野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏野同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看烟花的时候  要喊{\3c&H680B88&\4c&H2D042B&}玉屋{\r}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:39.89,TIPS1,NTP,0,0,0,,以前烟花商的名字  看烟花的时候叫这个名字来为其应援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想飞在天上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类果然不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓玉屋…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏野同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  木屐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚很疼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下吧  舞学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这样应该会舒服一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是平时也能对我这样温柔就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  左脚也伸出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  露露她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是刚才提到的phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙说过想喝波子汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露是怎样的女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你问我怎样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为感觉她总是会在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  偶尔不在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会感到非常平静
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.97,0:14:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很开朗活泼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有露露在总是非常热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人感到很累
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙真的不打算来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要帮她买波子汽水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过她那么小只  喝也喝不完
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好浪费钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有蚊子而已  蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭笨蛋晴彦  活该
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是去买下波子汽水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要买给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏野同学也要喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会再喝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  一会儿再喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花phantom出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.09,0:15:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要来奋力一炸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个吊坠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是烟花球phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.98,0:15:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快去安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要炸出大烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦  是烟花球phantom
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然在那么多人的地方胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要想办法阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.84,0:16:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧了它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是去烧烟花的话  会发生大爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小糸的声音用不上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  玲奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.65,0:16:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是吃了那种塞满火药的东西会吃坏肚子的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是舞姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花球phantom  弱点自然是水气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.14,0:16:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔布雷希特  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔布雷希特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来封印它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚金波…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉屋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:16:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.11,0:17:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  那个吊坠是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个烟花球phantom说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要炸出这一生最大的烟花  所以我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会这样大闹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能用亚伯梅林之指的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会让你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它想要排除妨碍自己实现愿望的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没什么办法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能把那个吊坠摘掉  魔法也就能解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吊坠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴彦  摘掉那个吊坠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  这样下去晴彦会被一起炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在那种地方  我们无计可施
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:17:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来想在喝完一瓶波子汽水之前保持这个大小的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  我是露露啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.22,0:18:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是露露吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.68,0:18:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没发现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也就是说那些悲惨往事  都是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能飞的就只有我  只能我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  为什么被抓住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.57,0:18:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.78,0:18:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想试试变大而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:50.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天骗了我一整天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说这个的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  取不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:19:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是在这种地方爆炸就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(483,1020)}我想炸出个超大的烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1386,1020)}我能理解你的心情  烟花球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,hana？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.61,0:19:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有请那个魔女phantom帮我实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然在实现之前就解开了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你还是可以实现愿望的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是能炸出超大烟花的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果在这种地方进行大爆炸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会给大家添麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去更高的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天一天非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不但能和晴彦一起那样并排走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有脚伤的处理也谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说了要喝波子汽水的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别走
